billEvents.eventText: REFERRED TO CORPORATIONS, AUTHORITIES AND COMMISSIONS

title: Enables the dormitory authority to finance and provide facilities for a research laboratory for epidemiology in Brooklyn
summary: Enables the dormitory authority to finance and provide facilities for a research laboratory for epidemiology in Brooklyn.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the public authorities law, in relation to and for the purpose of enabling the dormitory authority to finance and provide facilities for a research laboratory for epidemiology in the borough of Brooklyn
